.*    Author       : Ebon Clements                                           *
.*    Date         : 18/12/2003                                              *
.*    Modifications:                                                         *
.*         V9.03.01 25/02/2004  Sylvek Litewka  CAR 46508 & 46520            *
.*                  Added new fields to CCSEPSFD (from SDRG to CPAP).        *
.*                  Modified size of the new file and cleared new fields     *
.*                  before writing record.                                   *
.*         V9.03.00 18/12/2003         CAR                                   *
